{"tid":491044,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家認為呢次回調幾多？","createTime":"2017-12-06T06:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T15:39:19.000Z","uid":121126,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"04abb2ba2b272e132d194b7cc542ee8bd777da9b","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T06:45:28.000Z","msg":"假設真係第四浪深度回調，以我分析12月至1-2月有回調到25000-27000<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/144219_74b01b1fc84b836d20325d1fe71367aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F144219_74b01b1fc84b836d20325d1fe71367aa.jpg&h=a50f27bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打點睇呢次調整"},{"pid":"e1342f1d21e2fb1f055fa11ff27c6abcf59aa7e1","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"咁既跌幅分分鐘落到26000-25000"},{"pid":"bf875e3ec016b50b42f008ce76d8f9c02b7a1609","tid":491044,"uid":9506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:29:41.000Z","msg":"沈大師啱先講上30000點個浪已經係第五浪，同巴打你嘅數法有啲唔同。<br />\n我無惡意，純粹想知數波浪呢件事係咪都係靠主觀判斷？"},{"pid":"dab337523ce1af4e30e550477230acef7ec99967","tid":491044,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"3月前快手隊有咁深得咁深<br />\n我2隻熊仔3月到期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daed73bd28efd4317bb0c45a5212a06cd08a26aa","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沈大師啱先講上30000點個浪已經係第五浪，同巴打你嘅數法有啲唔同。<br />\n我無惡意，純粹想知數波浪呢件事係咪都係靠主觀判斷？</blockquote><br />\n因為拎一個升市既開始黎畫，以波浪理論基礎原理，第3浪多數係最長，仲有第4浪一般會係回調到0.382/0.5/0.618，第5浪必須會經過第4浪既回調，咩已經30000已經係第5浪根本唔符合基礎原理，都未有第4浪何來第5浪？"},{"pid":"62c7e49bcb1d5bd5bcd28b69f6abe2eeae3bfb18","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:36:18.000Z","msg":"我冇睇沈大師既野，係唔係佢講係第3浪既延伸浪中既第5浪？"},{"pid":"030ef97263288b45cb9b16374ecb72ec18479ceb","tid":491044,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:40:16.000Z","msg":"22000"},{"pid":"b19cf63675b1524aead97a6f260bbb5f6fa0f653","tid":491044,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沈大師啱先講上30000點個浪已經係第五浪，同巴打你嘅數法有啲唔同。<br />\n我無惡意，純粹想知數波浪呢件事係咪都係靠主觀判斷？</blockquote><br />\n因為拎一個升市既開始黎畫，以波浪理論基礎原理，第3浪多數係最長，仲有第4浪一般會係回調到0.382/0.5/0.618，第5浪必須會經過第4浪既回調，咩已經30000已經係第5浪根本唔符合基礎原理，都未有第4浪何來第5浪？</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係用黃金分割法？介唔介意講多少少點解你咁相信波浪理論同埋黃金分割法呢？"},{"pid":"856c5db45325d70d62acd07f9fbbbc5d9a482609","tid":491044,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"07年浪4 跌左4 5千點<br />\n好似係由23000左右 跌到落18000左右<br />\n之後就爆上31000<br />\n<br />\n不過波浪理論 當局中好難睇到<br />\n都係用黎馬後炮多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07564b442da666359843480c0585a0bcdd415dc","tid":491044,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我冇睇沈大師既野，係唔係佢講係第3浪既延伸浪中既第5浪？</blockquote><br />\n呢層無仔細留意，但係佢啱先喺電視係將升去30000點個浪畫成第五浪。"},{"pid":"628bc2ec336dca9e38e61a00a636ae7fc5fbe330","tid":491044,"uid":12440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700"},{"pid":"b808c783db9abe20b5f7b8c8bd33f39b54153ceb","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沈大師啱先講上30000點個浪已經係第五浪，同巴打你嘅數法有啲唔同。<br />\n我無惡意，純粹想知數波浪呢件事係咪都係靠主觀判斷？</blockquote><br />\n因為拎一個升市既開始黎畫，以波浪理論基礎原理，第3浪多數係最長，仲有第4浪一般會係回調到0.382/0.5/0.618，第5浪必須會經過第4浪既回調，咩已經30000已經係第5浪根本唔符合基礎原理，都未有第4浪何來第5浪？</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係用黃金分割法？介唔介意講多少少點解你咁相信波浪理論同埋黃金分割法呢？</blockquote><br />\n因為波浪理論既原理就係用黃金分割法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0a4ef6d4df7ab5a152647b9215941ea8f4dd85","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T14:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700</blockquote><br />\n如果咁畫真係可以畫到5浪，但個週期太長"},{"pid":"515648b677b58675a464c5c5010976c3780fe579","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700</blockquote><br />\n如果咁畫真係可以畫到5浪，但個週期太長</blockquote><br />\n但係以咁長週期既第5頂轉為abc調整浪一般有重大既因素令到骨牌式效應而開始轉趨為調整波，暫時睇唔到有咩重大因素"},{"pid":"fe44165c1be7a024f7c06eb8c3cb028ce0c82182","tid":491044,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700</blockquote><br />\n如果咁畫真係可以畫到5浪，但個週期太長</blockquote><br />\n但係以咁長週期既第5<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>頂轉為abc調整浪一般有重大既因素令到骨牌式效應而開始轉趨<span style=\"color: red;\">勢</span>為調整<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>，暫時睇唔到有咩重大因素</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e8957946ad35bf54b70ec0d9724de1fd3515308e","tid":491044,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>沈大師啱先講上30000點個浪已經係第五浪，同巴打你嘅數法有啲唔同。<br />\n我無惡意，純粹想知數波浪呢件事係咪都係靠主觀判斷？</blockquote><br />\n因為拎一個升市既開始黎畫，以波浪理論基礎原理，第3浪多數係最長，仲有第4浪一般會係回調到0.382/0.5/0.618，第5浪必須會經過第4浪既回調，咩已經30000已經係第5浪根本唔符合基礎原理，都未有第4浪何來第5浪？</blockquote><br />\n巴打你係用黃金分割法？介唔介意講多少少點解你咁相信波浪理論同埋黃金分割法呢？</blockquote><br />\n因為波浪理論既原理就係用黃金分割法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok 我參考下"},{"pid":"d5ca8670965a6e79cb8e9d1da0e74f598f320399","tid":491044,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:10:22.000Z","msg":"簡單d睇 如果未來一兩個星期突然大反彈<br />\n接近上次高位<br />\n我會認為係熊市前最後逃生門<br />\n<br />\n如果慢慢陰跌 反面似浪4"},{"pid":"700b4572904d0ac31bbf2c587ff363f060b4d1bf","tid":491044,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:11:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單d睇 如果未來一兩個星期突然大反彈<br />\n接近上次高位<br />\n我會認為係熊市前最後逃生門<br />\n<br />\n如果慢慢陰跌 反而似浪4</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e353325116054f2f375cc9584d7e473c17fa6fda","tid":491044,"uid":12440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700</blockquote><br />\n如果咁畫真係可以畫到5浪，但個週期太長</blockquote><br />\n但係以咁長週期既第5<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>頂轉為abc調整浪一般有重大既因素令到骨牌式效應而開始轉趨<span style=\"color: red;\">勢</span>為調整<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>，暫時睇唔到有咩重大因素</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇得簡單啲 <br />\n用7年數據 過左1.96個s.d.<br />\n過左95% confidence interval <br />\n就向下調 最低見返20700啦"},{"pid":"97c668720e22a97f59c2836adc78077c49aa07ee","tid":491044,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/07/225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F07%2F225506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4ea38af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n20700</blockquote><br />\n如果咁畫真係可以畫到5浪，但個週期太長</blockquote><br />\n但係以咁長週期既第5<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>頂轉為abc調整浪一般有重大既因素令到骨牌式效應而開始轉趨<span style=\"color: red;\">勢</span>為調整<span style=\"color: red;\">浪</span>，暫時睇唔到有咩重大因素</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n過幾日我再研究下，宜家學緊business modelling<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}